*exim-4.86_rc4 (29 Jun 2015)

  29 Jun 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.86_rc4.ebuild,
  -exim-4.86_rc2.ebuild:
  Bump to Exim 4.86 RC4

*exim-4.86_rc3 (22 Jun 2015)

  22 Jun 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.86_rc3.ebuild,
  -exim-4.86_rc1.ebuild:
  Bump to latest 4.86 RC3

*exim-4.86_rc2 (15 Jun 2015)

  15 Jun 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.86_rc2.ebuild:
  Bump to Exim 4.86 RC2

  11 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.85.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #550528

  09 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.85.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #550528

*exim-4.86_rc1 (08 Jun 2015)

  08 Jun 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.86_rc1.ebuild:
  Add Exim-4.86 RC1

  28 May 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.85.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #550528

  05 May 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +files/exim.rc9,
  -files/exim.rc7, exim-4.85.ebuild, files/exim.confd:
  Include tidying up Exim's hint databases, bug #262819.  Doesn't warrant a
  revbump since we've been doing without for ages

  21 Mar 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild,
  exim-4.85.ebuild:
  use dosbin instead of exeinto /usr/sbin/ && doexe

*exim-4.85 (13 Jan 2015)

  13 Jan 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.85.ebuild,
  -exim-4.85_rc4.ebuild:
  Version bump

  03 Jan 2015; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild,
  exim-4.85_rc4.ebuild:
  Re-add CDB support, thanks to Nico Erfurth in bug #534230

*exim-4.85_rc4 (30 Dec 2014)

  30 Dec 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.85_rc4.ebuild,
  -exim-4.85_rc3.ebuild:
  Bump 4.85 to RC4

  28 Dec 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild,
  exim-4.85_rc3.ebuild:
  Rename virtual/postgresql to dev-db/postgresql

*exim-4.85_rc3 (22 Dec 2014)

  22 Dec 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.85_rc3.ebuild,
  -exim-4.85_rc2.ebuild:
  Bump Exim 4.85 release candidate

*exim-4.85_rc2 (04 Dec 2014)

  04 Dec 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.85_rc2.ebuild,
  -exim-4.85_rc1.ebuild:
  Bump to 4.85 RC2

*exim-4.85_rc1 (18 Nov 2014)

  18 Nov 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.85_rc1.ebuild:
  Version bump to first release candidate for 4.85

  03 Nov 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Update PostgreSQL dependencies and/or checks to virtual/postgresql.

  02 Nov 2014; Sven Vermeulen <swift@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Remove sec-policy/selinux-* dependency from DEPEND but keep in RDEPEND (bug
  #527698)

  18 Oct 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> -exim-4.80.1-r2.ebuild,
  -exim-4.80.1-r3.ebuild, -exim-4.80.1.ebuild, -exim-4.82.1.ebuild:
  Cleanup, bug #524154, #517934

  18 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #524154

  18 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #524154

  17 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #524154

  09 Oct 2014; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild,
  exim-4.80.1-r2.ebuild, exim-4.80.1-r3.ebuild, exim-4.82.1.ebuild,
  exim-4.84.ebuild:
  The libperl ebuild is only a dummy and will be removed; libperl is provided
  by dev-lang/perl.

  05 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #524154

  05 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #524154

  01 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #524154

  01 Oct 2014; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #524154

  30 Sep 2014; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #524154).

  30 Sep 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Add back missing keywords, new deps have been masked to allow stabling

  30 Sep 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1-r2.ebuild,
  exim-4.80.1-r3.ebuild, exim-4.80.1.ebuild, exim-4.82.1.ebuild,
  exim-4.84.ebuild:
  Install patched config file, instead of original, bug #523892

