*exim-4.83_rc2 (06 Jun 2014)

  06 Jun 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.83_rc2.ebuild,
  -exim-4.83_rc1.ebuild:
  Version bump to 4.83 RC2

  30 May 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.83_rc1.ebuild:
  Don't deal with eximon twice, should fix bug #511836

  30 May 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.83_rc1.ebuild:
  Notify DSN users to remove dsn_process switches, by Marcin Mirosław, bug
  #511818

  30 May 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.83_rc1.ebuild:
  Workaround whitespace eaters

  30 May 2014; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> exim-4.83_rc1.ebuild:
  Whitespace

  29 May 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.83_rc1.ebuild:
  Add back dsearch, bug #511790

  29 May 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> -exim-4.82-r1.ebuild,
  -exim-4.82.ebuild:
  Remove vulnerable versions, bug #511686

