  Marked ~hppa (bug #489736).

*exim-4.82-r1 (03 Mar 2014)

  03 Mar 2014; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.82-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Add support for redis, by Marcin Mirosław, bug #489736

  30 Dec 2013; Naohiro Aota <naota@gentoo.org> exim-4.82.ebuild,
  files/exim-4.82-makefile-freebsd.patch:
  Add ~x86-fbsd. #235785

  01 Nov 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.82.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Make support for PKCS#11 optional with USE=gnutls, cleanup some legacy code

  30 Oct 2013; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> exim-4.82.ebuild:
  Marked ~hppa (bug #489676).

