*exim-4.80.1-r2 (27 Jul 2013)

  27 Jul 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +exim-4.80.1-r2.ebuild,
  +files/exim-submission.socket, +files/exim-submission_at.service,
  +files/exim.service, +files/exim.socket, +files/exim_at.service:
  Install unit file #470754 by Alexander Tsoy

  23 Jul 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1-r1.ebuild,
  exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Fix/improve locating MySQL and PostgreSQL libraries, patch by Alexander Tsoy
  in bug #477792

  23 Jul 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> files/exim.logrotate:
  Remove now useless sharedscripts from logrotate, thanks Alexander Tsoy

  23 Jul 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fix header installation, not bumping due to no current consumers

*exim-4.80.1-r1 (22 Jul 2013)

  22 Jul 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.80.1-r1.ebuild,
  files/exim.logrotate:
  Move pid-file to /run, bug #455346
  Drop unnecessary (and sometimes errors producing) postrotate SIGHUP, thanks
  Alexander Tsoy, bug #477748
  Add dlfunc USE-flag to allow external dlfunc libraries to be compiled,
  based on patch by Marcin Mirosław, bug #436406
  Bump to EAPI4 to use REQUIRED_USE for spf and srs USE-flags, bug #447418

  23 Mar 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Set sensible default for relay_from_hosts when IPv6 is enabled, bug #448314

  23 Mar 2013; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Fix tidydb url in postinst, by Vladimir Varlamov, bug #462280

  28 Feb 2013; Jason A. Donenfeld <zx2c4@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Block opensmtpd.

  11 Nov 2012; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> -exim-4.76-r1.ebuild,
  -exim-4.76.ebuild, -exim-4.77.ebuild, -exim-4.80.ebuild,
  -files/exim-4.75-makefile-freebsd.patch, -files/exim-4.76-as-needed.patch,
  -files/exim.rc6:
  Drop vulnerable versions, bug #439734

  11 Nov 2012; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  ia64/sparc stable wrt #439734

  06 Nov 2012; Eray Aslan <eras@gentoo.org> exim-4.76-r1.ebuild,
  exim-4.76.ebuild, exim-4.77.ebuild, exim-4.80.1.ebuild, exim-4.80.ebuild:
  mail-mta/nbsmtp is no longer in the tree - remove from DEPEND

  04 Nov 2012; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org>
  +files/exim-4.80-spool-mail-group.patch, exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Deliver as group mail such that we can create new mail by default in
  /var/spool/mail, bug #438606 by DominikBuerkle

  30 Oct 2012; <swift@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild, exim-4.76-r1.ebuild,
  exim-4.77.ebuild, exim-4.80.ebuild, exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Adding SELinux dependency towards selinux-exim module

  30 Oct 2012; Andreas Schuerch <nativemad@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, see bug 439734

  29 Oct 2012; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  stable ppc ppc64, bug #439734

