  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #439734

*exim-4.80.1 (26 Oct 2012)

  26 Oct 2012; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.80.1.ebuild:
  Bump to 4.80.1 for DKIM security CVE-2012-5671.  Fixed use of AR and RANLIB,
  bug #438326

