*exim-4.77 (10 Oct 2011)

  10 Oct 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> -exim-4.77_rc4.ebuild,
  +exim-4.77.ebuild:
  Version bump to 4.77, contains incompatible changes in expansion conditions,
  see https://lists.exim.org/lurker/message/20111010.055624.f24c5ae2.en.html

*exim-4.77_rc4 (08 Oct 2011)

  08 Oct 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.77_rc4.ebuild,
  +files/exim-4.77-makefile-freebsd.patch:
  Add 4.77 RC4, masked

  16 Aug 2011; Christian Ruppert <idl0r@gentoo.org> files/exim.rc7:
  Get a rid of the deprecated start-stop-daemon commands, bug 372671.

*exim-4.76-r1 (03 Aug 2011)

  03 Aug 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> +exim-4.76-r1.ebuild,
  +files/exim-4.76-crosscompile.patch, +files/exim.rc7:
  Add patch to allow cross-compilation (bug #266591), add support for multiple
  exim instances to the init script (bug #376569).  Remove old and
  vulnerable versions.

  04 Jul 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild,
  +files/exim-4.76-as-needed.patch:
  Fix linking order such that linking works correctly with as-needed, bug
  #352265

  03 Jul 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org>
  files/exim-4.74-localscan_dlopen.patch:
  add spaces around LFLAGS assignment, not to confuse make, bug #352265

  16 May 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #366369).

  14 May 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #366369

  14 May 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild:
  ppc/ppc64 stable wrt #366369

  14 May 2011; Thomas Kahle <tomka@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild:
  x86 stable per bug 366369

  13 May 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> exim-4.76.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #366369

